BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (One day, Owen faced his hardest truth yet. His best friend Marcus asked him, 'Do you like) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (my new haircut?') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (Owen didn't love it. But the old Owen would have said something mean, and the lying Owen) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (would have said something false.) Tj ET
