BT /F2 11 Tf 54 716.0 Td (Page 25) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (And here's the thing Owen learned that he wants YOU to know:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (Everyone is tempted to lie sometimes. It feels easier in the moment.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (But lies don't just disappear. They grow. They follow you. They push people away.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (The truth might be harder to say, but it builds something precious   trust.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td (And trust, once you earn it, makes every relationship in your life stronger and more) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (beautiful than any lie ever could.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 596.4 Td ([Illustration: A final image showing Owen as a young boy looking directly at the reader) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 582.4 Td (with an honest, warm smile, no shadow in sight, standing in bright sunlight, a trustworthy) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 568.4 Td (and happy person]) Tj ET
endstream
