stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (The Moral of the Story) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 674.2 Td (Honesty Builds Trust; Lies Break It) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 646.4 Td (Owen learned that lies might seem like easy shortcuts, but they grow into something dark) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 632.4 Td (and heavy that pushes everyone away. The truth can be scary to tell, especially when you) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 618.4 Td (might get in trouble. But honesty builds trust   and trust is the foundation of every) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 604.4 Td (friendship, every family, and every relationship. When people trust you, they believe in) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 590.4 Td (you, count on you, and want to be near you. That's worth more than any 'easy' lie.) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
