BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Discussion Questions for Parents) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 680.2 Td (After reading this story together, talk about these questions:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 656.4 Td (1. Have you ever told a lie that made you feel bad afterward? What happened?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 632.6 Td (2. Why do you think people stop trusting someone who lies a lot?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 608.8 Td (3. What's the difference between a time when telling the truth is easy and when it's hard?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 585.0 Td (4. If Owen's shadow appeared behind YOUR lies, how big do you think it would be right now?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 561.2 Td (5. How can you practice being more honest, even when the truth is hard to say?) Tj ET
endstream
